{
  "stem": "294.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, it's funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In-- [SIGHS] was it in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, no, it could not be in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In-- in Auschwitz-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think it was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had two bunk mates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, they were two girls from a very small town in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Twins, but they didn't look at all like each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we were ready, when they came to take us, you know, they notified us that-- they told our whole group to get together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they-- the told us we're going on the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We still didn't know if we're going to Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these girl-- girls, the two girls, started to pray, Shema Yisrael.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know this is a prayer, the Jewish Hebrew prayer to God, may have mercy on us and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the first time I ever heard it, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I thought, what a wonderful thing it is to have faith like this in the middle of this hell, to pray like they did.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they took us on the trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the conditions were even worse when we arrived-- when we arrived from Plaszow to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Terrible, and we were exhausted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were-- we-- we were all very sick, still, you know, and cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we arriving after maybe two nights and one day, or vice versa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No water.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We arriving--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was already-- no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was still-- oh, it must have been December, because we were three weeks in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it must have been December already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very cold.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arriving in Bruennlitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We still don't know that this is Bruennlitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
